text: Guthrie is an unincorporated community and census-designated place (CDP) in the U.S. state of Texas. It is the county seat of King County. In 2020, 151 people lived there. It is found 142 km east of Lubbock. Category:Census- designated places in Texas Category:Unincorporated communities in Texas Category:County seats in Texas
title: Guthrie, Texas
